           move      1                    to   w-stu-rrr-pnt-stu      .
       exe-pgm-bkg-200.
           move      spaces               to   w-stu-rrr-255-byt      .
           move      w-stu-rrr-pnt-stu    to   w-stu-rrr-sav-pnt      .
           unstring  rr                   into w-stu-rrr-255-byt
                                  with pointer w-stu-rrr-pnt-stu      .
